<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.2">
<l>taiya lāḷmēl kātalceyta tāṉavaṉ vāḷarakkaṉ</l>
<l>poyyi lāta poṉmuṭika ḷoṉpatō ṭoṉṟumaṉṟu</l>
<l>ceyta vempōr taṉṉilaṅkōr ceñcarat tāluruḷa</l>
<l>veyta ventai yemperumā ṉevvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Our] great lord, our father who shot with a red[-hot] arrow</l>
<l>There in heated battle which he conducted that day,</l>
<l>So that the nine-and-one genuine golden crowns rolled</l>
<l rend="indent">[from] the sword-demon,</l>
<l>The Dānava who acted [with] lust toward the lady,</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one who lies in Evvuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
